  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- all together, I had to know if-- right in a short time I had 20 with this-- with this sickness.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I isolated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I said it is a-- they have diarrheas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans, we had not under-- who are under control of the Luftwaffe, of the-- of the people--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--people from-- from the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shortly after we came, came a major.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he called me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he introduced, I am [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am the [GERMAN] commandant-- commandant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I hope that you are satisfied with the quarters what you have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would like to give you more food, but I get rationed that food what-- what I-- I-- I get.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot get more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you have warm-- warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I supply you with-- with-- with-- with wood, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I realize it is a man who is a friendly man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He would--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dear, you know, why-- why-- the same thing happened with this-- with this thing, you know, what-- what-- became so famous?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same analog.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two years-- although, later we were managed by the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- the people worked at the airport-- airport, and a still strong connection, you know, with our-- our camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To work at the airport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Please, for them, the airports were not big enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- right away-- [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Riga ?] was the big offensive against Leningrad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they moved soldiers by air.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was rather small, so they had to enlarge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, it is over 1,000 people, who were Jews, is working at the airport to enlarge the airport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything going to-- to enlarge the airport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] With this, [NON-ENGLISH] with this, he [INAUDIBLE] who sent, you know, to manage us inside was [SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was sergeant--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sergeant-- very friendly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the [INAUDIBLE] was managed by Obergefreiter Schumacher-- face of a murderer, but who revealed to be a very fine man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All major sent us sent these men, who he selected under condition that you will be good to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The doctor from-- [INAUDIBLE] medication, I had problem with medications.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sergeant, gets up and says, let's go to the-- to the-- [GERMAN], means small hospital, the German, at the airport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got acquainted with the-- the doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the doctor even asked me-- invite-- invited me to a breakfast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For me, it was unusual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was-- They addressed us not-- not the, not you-- you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They addressed us like animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here I see a completely different attitude.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dear, every day would come approximately each morning, among the 300 in the beginning, around 15, 20, will come for these-- these complaints.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I had always, you know, around 10 not working-- 10, 20 not working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we came, men and women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not many-- few were pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- right away, I was told that if a woman-- at the beginning, it was no problem.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When she's pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But soon, you know, the SS took over [? also. ?] And if, you know, SS gets informed that a woman is pregnant and gives birth to a child, she will be killed, and the child will be killed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I order, told, you know, please, whoever is pregnant, come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will terminate the pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm an obstetrician gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's my field.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was doing abortions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm doing abortion not now for my camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not far away, was so-called [NON-ENGLISH] camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were also men and women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I don't recall how many-- 500, also pregnancies-- everybody, Klebanow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was in this respect-- it was all the [? beginning ?] army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was very fine attitude.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had to do-- to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will tell you, the greatest amount, it was in '44, in July.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got 2,000 Hungarian women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into mine-- Spilwe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spilwe is a tremendous brewery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have places to bring them, to give them a place where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have straw-- straw sacks-- straw sacks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody had a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And among this, I had around-- I announced right away, who is pregnant to come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had 20 some pregnancies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I recall, I worked with my wife [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Doing abortions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Saving their lives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gustav Sorge was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nazi nickname-- nickname, 'the Iron Gustav.' The other--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He became commandant of our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when I came [INAUDIBLE] first time with a pregnancy, and I came to him and I say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hauptscharfuhrer, I examined the one, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and she's pregnant.",
